        "TINMOUTH": "The crappie. [U.S.]",
        "TINNEN": "Made or consisting of tin. [Obs.]",
        "TINNIENT": "Emitting a clear sound. [Obs.]",
        "TINNITUS": "A ringing, whistling, or other imaginary noise perceived in theears; -- called also tinnitus aurium.",
