        "TRADUCIANISM": "The doctrine that human souls are produced by the act ofgeneration; -- opposed to creationism, and infusionism.",
        "TRADUCINGLY": "In a traducing manner; by traduction; slanderously.",
        "TRADUCT": "To derive or deduce; also, to transmit; to transfer. [Obs.]Fotherby.",
